name: Chaetoceros deflandrei
comment: Latitude approximate. Based on information from Jacques (1983), Fiala & Oriol (1984), & Fiala & Oriol (1990), there are 5 possible isolation locations, all along the same longitude: 48S, 54S, 58S, 60S, and 65S. In the absence of further information from the authors, I have used the median location.
